          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.625 9.75a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375m-13.5 3.01c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.087.16 2.185.283 3.293.369V21l4.184-4.183a1.14 1.14 0 01.778-.332 48.294 48.294 0 005.83-.498c1.585-.233 2.708-1.626 2.708-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-1">Have a question?</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-2">Contact the owner directly to ask about the boat or your trip.</p>
                <button id="contact-owner-btn-sidebar"
                  class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors"
                  data-owner-id="${esc(ownerId)}"
